<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I loved how the author provided the experience so deeply regarding Aoife and what she saw/didn't see in words. Since she responded with a smile and a <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I loved how the author provided the experience so deeply regarding Aoife and what she saw/didn't see in words. Since she responded with a smile and a should shrug, which he was upset by for obvious reasons, I was wondering if it was "Do you love me?".<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
